headline: ADM Named to FORTUNE Magazine’s 2026 Most Admired Company List
summary: CHICAGO, January 22, 2026--ADM (NYSE: ADM) has been named one of the world’s most admired companies in the food production industry by FORTUNE Magazine for 2026.
